-- Obama: Chance of consumer-driven recovery less likely
-- 
-- Mon Oct 4, 2010 3:17pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/10/04/us-obama-recovery-idUSTRE6934X220101004

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - President Barack Obama said on Monday the prospect of a consumer-driven, "V-shaped" economic recovery was less likely because Americans were trying to save more and reduce debt in the aftermath of a deep recession. (Reporting by  Matt Spetalnick ) 

